README
======

This is the resources used to generate formulae in PBFVMC as presented in
the paper:
   "PBFVMC: A New Pseudo-Boolean Formulation to Virtual-Machine Consolidation"

Following folders contains:

  - pbfvmc-formulae/
      - All formulae used in the paper divided per amount of available
        hardware

  - pbfvmc-generator/
      - Software used to generate pseudo-Boolean formulae
      - This folder contains a simple example and all description files used
        to generate formulae used in the paper.

If you have any comments or doubts don't hesitate to contact me at
brunoribas@gmail.com
